---
title: Sweet 'n Sour Meatballs with Pineapple and Green Peppers
description: Making your own sweet 'n sour sauce couldn't be easier, and our meatballs are simmered right in the sauce! We've even added a secret ingredient into our meatballs - flaxmeal. This ingredient not only helps to hold the meatballs together, it's also high in heart-healthy omega 3's!
